%% ANALYSIS

% Before we start, Matlab shitty import has a SUPERFUCKINANNOYING feature
% where it imports differently if you use the automated script rather than
% their GUI. It turns the COM column into a mix of 'char' and 'doubles'
% which makes it super hard to manipulate. This wasted like and hour and
% a half of my damn time trying to figure out why they weren't indexing
